  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/FSKit\/FSItem\/Attribute\/type\ncrawled: 2026-03-10T15:49:05Z\n---\n\n# type\n\n**Type Property**\n\nThe type attribute.\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\nstatic var type: FSItem.Attribute { get }\n```\n\n## Working with metadata attributes\n\n- **mode**: The mode attribute.\n- **linkCount**: The link count attribute.\n- **uid**: The user ID (uid) attribute.\n- **gid**: The group ID (gid) attribute.\n- **flags**: The flags attribute.\n- **size**: The size attribute.\n- **allocSize**: The allocated size attribute.\n- **supportsLimitedXAttrs**: The supports limited extended attributes attribute.\n- **inhibitKernelOffloadedIO**: The inhibit kernel offloaded I\/O attribute.\n\n",
